            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Langkawi Mangrove & Island Hopping Tours"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Discover the very best of Langkawi in one value-packed experience! This island hopping &amp; mangrove tour is one of the best, cheapest, and most safety-focused packages available on redBus which is perfect for travelers who want to explore more while spending less.Journey through Langkawi’s breathtaking highlands and uncover the island’s hidden gems, then cruise into the heart of its enchanting mangrove forests. From dramatic landscapes and lush greenery to serene waterways and unique wildlife, this tour brings you deep into the natural beauty of Langkawi Island."
          }
        ]
      },
