            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Enjoy a scenic boat ride across Langkawi’s crystal-clear waters with stunning views of surrounding islands.Visit multiple iconic islands, including stops for photo-taking, sightseeing, and light exploration (subject to sea and weather conditions).Experience Langkawi’s natural beauty up close, from limestone formations to lush greenery and open sea views.Relax and enjoy the ride with experienced boat operators who prioritize safety and comfort.Learn interesting facts and local insights shared by the guide during the tour."
              }
